<title>USA: Peerless Industrial in talks on sale.</title>
<headline>Peerless Industrial in talks on sale.</headline>
<dateline>MINNEAPOLIS 1997-03-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Peerless Industrial Group Inc on Friday said it was in negotiations with a party that may purchase all of its outstanding common stock for $1.67 per share in cash.</p>
<p>The company in a statement did not identify the potential buyer.</p>
<p>Peerless shares closed on Thursday at 1-5/8.</p>
<p>While the company is engaged in discussions with the potential buyer, there can be no assurance that an acquisition will occur, the company said.</p>
